rComments: Fantastic teacher. Extremely friendly, laid back, and interesting. Though some of the readings are pretty dense, she REALLY helps you to fully understand them through lecture and discussion. I would definitely take another one of her classes.
Sarah's the best. Friendly, smart, easy to learn from if you're actually engaged with the material; it seems like those who haven't liked her just haven't been engaged.
Sarah is helpful and encouraging to her students. Pushes you hard, but makes you want to meet her expectations.
